## Installation
Currently, `Fold.ai` is not available on any package manager platforms. The release version has been built as native JavaScript and can be run directly using Node.js.

```
#1. Manually install project dependencies
cd fold
npm install
Node bin/server.js

#2. Windows users can use `dependency_install.bat` for one-click startup
Double-click the .bat file

#3. Linux / MacOS users can use the .sh script to install dependencies and start
Double-click the .sh file
```

